              <a class="list-group-item" href="http://greatfutures.org/pages/waystogive.aspx?_ga=1.12737010.43999393.1478702949" target="_blank">Boys & Girls Clubs of America</a>
              <a class="list-group-item" href="https://secure3.convio.net/cfrr/site/Donation2;jsessionid=97A4C7A9488B5DDF3450546DE1123DB2.app347a?1380.donation=form1&df_id=1380&web&_ga=1.145398384.513337705.1476995534" target="_blank">Center for Reproductive Rights</a>
